{
  "stem": "766.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first five days-- now it will come, what happened to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, one day came over there a German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot her name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was with the-- with the dog and with the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with the whip.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she asked who knows to sing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a Greek girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't cut her hair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had long hair.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe the-- only the-- the-- [NON-ENGLISH], the East Jews, they did it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Hungarian, also, didn't have shaved, cut short.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But only we.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she says, who knows to sing?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was the Greek girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she stepped out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was singing 'Ave Maria.' And this German, head was leaning against the wall.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And tears were running down from emotion.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, maybe some transformation will come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because she was known as a devil with the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with the whip and with the dog.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this 'Ave Maria,' and the tears, I thought, no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the girl finished, she started beating her with the whip after this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe because she-- she's so-- she sang so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Couldn't tell [? her age. ?]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- in this block were only Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So to show you a German intelligence, they are musical.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they love music.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was emotional and very moved with 'Ave Maria.' But later, the-- the-- the hatred came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she, almost-- and this were a kid, the girl.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, one day came somebody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can't remember, military or not military man and said, are there here, some doctors?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were four from our town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one was with the sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One was with the daughter and one was-- I don't remember, and I.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they took me because I was alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm the [NON-ENGLISH], [? the ?] [? person. ?]",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
